  "mode": {
    "values": [
      "fast",
      "balanced",
      "deep"
    ],
    "source_url": "https://keirolabs.cloud/",
    "comment": "v2 search endpoints exposed through `mode`: balanced uses `/api/v2/keirolabs`, fast/deep use `/api/v2/search/fast`, and content requests use `/api/v2/search/content`. KeiroLabs expects the API key in the JSON body."
